[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Privacy Policy" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:30px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:43px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1536150978588{padding-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Summary:" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:20px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:43px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]business takes technology to businesses, consumers and, society in a way that makes amazing experiences possible but doesn’t come at the expense of your privacy. We believe in change and performance that supports your privacy rights and in technology designed with those rights in mind.

In particular, this Separation Notice explains how our goods, services and, technologies use your personal information. It applies to our use of personal information across our websites, products, online services, software, apps, tools, and other services and functionality we provide, both online and offline (collectively referred to as “Havnor® Services”), unless a separate, or supplementary, privacy notice is offered. See “Additional Privacy Notices and Supplements” for additional information posted for specific Havnor® Services. at <a href="https://www.havnor.com/en-us/locations/">https://www.havnor.com/en-us/locations/</a>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1536151740300{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;border-bottom-width: 1px !important;border-left-width: 1px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;border-left-color: #e5e5e5 !important;border-left-style: solid !important;border-right-color: #e5e5e5 !important;border-right-style: solid !important;border-top-color: #e5e5e5 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;border-bottom-color: #e5e5e5 !important;border-bottom-style: solid !important;}"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="1. Personal Data Privacy - General" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539089630567{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 Havnor collects information as part of its business operations, to provide services, to respond to requests and offer customer support, to fulfill legal and contractual responsibilities and to develop its innovative products. You provide some of this data directly, such as when you order an Havnor product, contact customer support, or register for an Havnor event or publication. We also collect information into your interaction with Havnor® Services and our website, for example, using embedded product technologies and cookies. We also obtain data from third parties.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dcdcdc"][vc_custom_heading text="2. Information You Provide to Havnor Voluntarily" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539089681678{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 When you subscribe to a newsletter, create an account, make a purchase or request information from Havnor, we will ask for things like contact, billing, shipping and communication information, payment card or financial account data, and account ID or credentials in order to fulfill your request. If you visit one of our stores or locations, attend a trade show or event, or otherwise contact us, you may also voluntarily provide similar information.

Interactive stories in some Havnor Services may allow you to invite friends, follow others, comment on or make unique posts, or share photos, video or other personal content. When you affirmatively share this content, we may collect and use it in accordance with this Notice. Additionally, by way of your social action, we may receive information about you from another user, such as when your friend posts content that includes you.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dcdcdc"][vc_custom_heading text="3. Device and Product Operation" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539089704101{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 If you download and use certain Havnor Service like software or an app, we may track and collect usage data, such as when the software or app accesses our servers, what information and files have been downloaded through the use of the software or app, and how you interact with the software or app during use. Some of this data may be protected as personal information under applicable data protection laws.

